            "id": "devotion",
            "type": "devotion",
            "title": "Daily Devotional",
            "value": "%3Cp%3EHow%20easy%20it%20is%20for%20us%20to%20hear%20a%20word%20from%20the%20Lord%20and%20decide%20that%20it%20does%20not%20apply%20to%20our%20lives%20or%20that%20it%20is%20not%20for%20today!%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EPashhur%2C%20the%20priest%20in%20charge%20of%20the%20temple%20of%20the%20Lord%2C%20despised%20Jeremiah's%20prophecies%20against%20the%20detestable%20practice%20of%20sacrificing%20children%20to%20Baal%20in%20the%20valley%20of%20Topheth%20(Jeremiah%2020%3A1-2).%20This%20horrible%20ritual%20took%20place%20with%20the%20heathen%20priests%20of%20Baal%20beating%20drums%20to%20drown%20out%20the%20screams%20of%20little%20babies%20being%20burned%20alive.%20Jeremiah%20said%20that%20performing%20such%20atrocities%20never%20entered%20God's%20mind%20(19%3A5).%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EHumankind%20can%20stoop%20to%20some%20terrible%20deeds%20when%20there%20is%20no%20voice%20of%20reason.%20Jeremiah%20saw%20this%20dreadful%20scene%20of%20infant%20sacrifice%20and%20prophesied%20the%20destruction%20of%20Judah%20and%20Jerusalem.%20When%20Pashhur%20threatened%20him%2C%20Jeremiah%20said%2C%20%22I%20can't%20stop!%20If%20I%20say%20I'll%20never%20mention%20the%20Lord%20or%20speak%20in%20his%20name%2C%20his%20word%20burns%20in%20my%20heart%20like%20a%20fire.%20It's%20like%20a%20fire%20in%20my%20bones!%20I%20am%20weary%20of%20holding%20it%20in!%22%20(20%3A9).%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EWe%20should%20not%20despise%20prophecy%2C%20but%20invite%20it.%20We%20should%20pray%20for%20God%20to%20give%20us%20voices%20in%20our%20nation%20to%20proclaim%20the%20truth%20before%20it%20is%20too%20late.%20The%20lives%20we%20save%20may%20be%20our%20own.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%0A"
        },
        {
            "id": "ot-passage",
            "type": "passage",
            "title": "Old Testament Reading",
            "api_nlt_to_ref": "Jeremiah.19:1-21:14",
            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3EJeremiah%2019%3A1-21%3A14%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_19_1%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2219%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3EJeremiah%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E19%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EJeremiah%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Shattered%20Jar%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-ch-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3EThis%20is%20what%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20said%20to%20me%3A%20%26%23x201C%3BGo%20and%20buy%20a%20clay%20jar.%20Then%20ask%20some%20of%20the%20leaders%20of%20the%20people%20and%20of%20the%20priests%20to%20follow%20you.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_19_2%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2219%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3EGo%20out%20through%20the%20Gate%20of%20Broken%20Pots%20to%20the%20garbage%20dump%20in%20the%20valley%20of%20Ben-Hinnom%2C%20and%20give%20them%20this%20message.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_19_3%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2219%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3ESay%20to%20them%2C%20%26%23x2018%3BListen%20to%20this%20message%20from%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20you%20kings%20of%20Judah%20and%20citizens%20of%20Jerusalem!%20This%20is%20what%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20of%20Heaven%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Armies%2C%20the%20God%20of%20Israel%2C%20says%3A%20I%20will%20bring%20a%20terrible%20disaster%20on%20this%20place%2C%20and%20the%20ears%20of%20those%20who%20hear%20about%20it%20will%20ring!%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_19_4%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2219%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3B%26%23x2018%3BFor%20Israel%20has%20forsaken%20me%20and%20turned%20this%20valley%20into%20a%20place%20of%20wickedness.%20The%20people%20burn%20incense%20to%20foreign%20gods%26%23x2014%3Bidols%20never%20before%20acknowledged%20by%20this%20generation%2C%20by%20their%20ancestors%2C%20or%20by%20the%20kings%20of%20Judah.%20And%20they%20have%20filled%20this%20place%20with%20the%20blood%20of%20innocent%20children.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_19_5%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2219%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3EThey%20have%20built%20pagan%20shrines%20to%20Baal%2C%20and%20there%20they%20burn%20their%20sons%20as%20sacrifices%20to%20Baal.%20I%20have%20never%20commanded%20such%20a%20horrible%20deed%3B%20it%20never%20even%20crossed%20my%20mind%20to%20command%20such%20a%20thing!%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_19_6%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2219%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20beware%2C%20for%20the%20time%20is%20coming%2C%20says%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20when%20this%20garbage%20dump%20will%20no%20longer%20be%20called%20Topheth%20or%20the%20valley%20of%20Ben-Hinnom%2C%20but%20the%20Valley%20of%20Slaughter.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_19_7%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2219%22%20vn%3D%227%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3B%26%23x2018%3BFor%20I%20will%20upset%20the%20careful%20plans%20of%20Judah%20and%20Jerusalem.%20I%20will%20allow%20the%20people%20to%20be%20slaughtered%20by%20invading%20armies%2C%20and%20I%20will%20leave%20their%20dead%20bodies%20as%20food%20for%20the%20vultures%20and%20wild%20animals.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_19_8%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2219%22%20vn%3D%228%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3EI%20will%20reduce%20Jerusalem%20to%20ruins%2C%20making%20it%20a%20monument%20to%20their%20stupidity.%20All%20who%20pass%20by%20will%20be%20astonished%20and%20will%20gasp%20at%20the%20destruction%20they%20see%20there.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_19_9%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2219%22%20vn%3D%229%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E9%3C%2Fspan%3EI%20will%20see%20to%20it%20that%20your%20enemies%20lay%20siege%20to%20the%20city%20until%20all%20the%20food%20is%20gone.%20Then%20those%20trapped%20inside%20will%20eat%20their%20own%20sons%20and%20daughters%20and%20friends.%20They%20will%20be%20driven%20to%20utter%20despair.%26%23x2019%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_19_10%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2219%22%20vn%3D%2210%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E10%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BAs%20these%20men%20watch%20you%2C%20Jeremiah%2C%20smash%20the%20jar%20you%20brought.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_19_11%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2219%22%20vn%3D%2211%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E11%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20say%20to%20them%2C%20%26%23x2018%3BThis%20is%20what%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20of%20Heaven%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Armies%20says%3A%20As%20this%20jar%20lies%20shattered%2C%20so%20I%20will%20shatter%20the%20people%20of%20Judah%20and%20Jerusalem%20beyond%20all%20hope%20of%20repair.%20They%20will%20bury%20the%20bodies%20here%20in%20Topheth%2C%20the%20garbage%20dump%2C%20until%20there%20is%20no%20more%20room%20for%20them.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_19_12%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2219%22%20vn%3D%2212%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E12%3C%2Fspan%3EThis%20is%20what%20I%20will%20do%20to%20this%20place%20and%20its%20people%2C%20says%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E.%20I%20will%20cause%20this%20city%20to%20become%20defiled%20like%20Topheth.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_19_13%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2219%22%20vn%3D%2213%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E13%3C%2Fspan%3EYes%2C%20all%20the%20houses%20in%20Jerusalem%2C%20including%20the%20palace%20of%20Judah%26%23x2019%3Bs%20kings%2C%20will%20become%20like%20Topheth%26%23x2014%3Ball%20the%20houses%20where%20you%20burned%20incense%20on%20the%20rooftops%20to%20your%20star%20gods%2C%20and%20where%20liquid%20offerings%20were%20poured%20out%20to%20your%20idols.%26%23x2019%3B%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_19_14%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2219%22%20vn%3D%2214%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E14%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20Jeremiah%20returned%20from%20Topheth%2C%20the%20garbage%20dump%20where%20he%20had%20delivered%20this%20message%2C%20and%20he%20stopped%20in%20front%20of%20the%20Temple%20of%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E.%20He%20said%20to%20the%20people%20there%2C%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_19_15%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2219%22%20vn%3D%2215%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E15%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BThis%20is%20what%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20of%20Heaven%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Armies%2C%20the%20God%20of%20Israel%2C%20says%3A%20%26%23x2018%3BI%20will%20bring%20disaster%20upon%20this%20city%20and%20its%20surrounding%20towns%20as%20I%20promised%2C%20because%20you%20have%20stubbornly%20refused%20to%20listen%20to%20me.%26%23x2019%3B%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_20_1%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2220%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3EJeremiah%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EJeremiah%20and%20Pashhur%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-ch-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3ENow%20Pashhur%20son%20of%20Immer%2C%20the%20priest%20in%20charge%20of%20the%20Temple%20of%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20heard%20what%20Jeremiah%20was%20prophesying.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_20_2%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2220%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20he%20arrested%20Jeremiah%20the%20prophet%20and%20had%20him%20whipped%20and%20put%20in%20stocks%20at%20the%20Benjamin%20Gate%20of%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Temple.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_20_3%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2220%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20next%20day%2C%20when%20Pashhur%20finally%20released%20him%2C%20Jeremiah%20said%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BPashhur%2C%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20has%20changed%20your%20name.%20From%20now%20on%20you%20are%20to%20be%20called%20%26%23x2018%3BThe%20Man%20Who%20Lives%20in%20Terror.%26%23x2019%3B%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E20%3A3%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3EMagor-missabib%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20which%20means%20%26%23x201C%3Bsurrounded%20by%20terror%26%23x201D%3B%3B%20also%20in%2020%3A10.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_20_4%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2220%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3EFor%20this%20is%20what%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20says%3A%20%26%23x2018%3BI%20will%20send%20terror%20upon%20you%20and%20all%20your%20friends%2C%20and%20you%20will%20watch%20as%20they%20are%20slaughtered%20by%20the%20swords%20of%20the%20enemy.%20I%20will%20hand%20the%20people%20of%20Judah%20over%20to%20the%20king%20of%20Babylon.%20He%20will%20take%20them%20captive%20to%20Babylon%20or%20run%20them%20through%20with%20the%20sword.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_20_5%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2220%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3EAnd%20I%20will%20let%20your%20enemies%20plunder%20Jerusalem.%20All%20the%20famed%20treasures%20of%20the%20city%26%23x2014%3Bthe%20precious%20jewels%20and%20gold%20and%20silver%20of%20your%20kings%26%23x2014%3Bwill%20be%20carried%20off%20to%20Babylon.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_20_6%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2220%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3EAs%20for%20you%2C%20Pashhur%2C%20you%20and%20all%20your%20household%20will%20go%20as%20captives%20to%20Babylon.%20There%20you%20will%20die%20and%20be%20buried%2C%20you%20and%20all%20your%20friends%20to%20whom%20you%20prophesied%20that%20everything%20would%20be%20all%20right.%26%23x2019%3B%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_20_7%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2220%22%20vn%3D%227%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EJeremiah%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Complaint%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3EO%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20you%20misled%20me%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20I%20allowed%20myself%20to%20be%20misled.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EYou%20are%20stronger%20than%20I%20am%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20you%20overpowered%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3ENow%20I%20am%20mocked%20every%20day%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eeveryone%20laughs%20at%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_20_8%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2220%22%20vn%3D%228%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3EWhen%20I%20speak%2C%20the%20words%20burst%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3E%26%23x201C%3BViolence%20and%20destruction!%26%23x201D%3B%20I%20shout.%3C%2Fp%3E%0